title: The Uncanny Valley
description: Casey and Danielle are gifted with the presence of Charles Rogers (Search Party) and unlike Sonya's sad dinner party food, his takes are anything but dry. We talk Rinna Rose and Rinna Rage, Erika's dominatrix dreams, and visual penis lines. Plus is Taylor what OC needs? And does she deserve the orange? All questions will be answered, but will also leave us even more confused.
